{"tid":1977750,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[DSE] 想問下考埸規矩","createTime":"2020-04-18T07:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T06:25:34.000Z","uid":257285,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5ebf7f2c353163c8ee55488ea2015dfb63da3308","tid":1977750,"uid":257285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:48:53.000Z","msg":"仲有唔夠十日就要正式開始啦<br />\n始終一次校外mock都冇試過考，所以真係驚會犯左啲咩規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想問下，可唔可以帶智能手錶架？<br />\n聽講係唔可以帶apple watch嗰啲<br />\n但亦都有聽過人過佢唔會check得咁嚴,唔洗咁驚<br />\n如果真係唔俾帶，咁就要及早買定電子錶<br />\n<br />\n最後順便講句<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加油呀各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n各位中學手足今年我哋<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />是敵但也是友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03cba5ddfaa5cbbe4b190ec7026f3a4aa5f8570a","tid":1977750,"uid":54721,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:51:13.000Z","msg":"你自己再諗清楚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456d495b7cf89bd2cc3e92b4507f9aa005ecb3d2","tid":1977750,"uid":2660,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:51:26.000Z","msg":"iwatch會要你除<br />\n之後擺係枱底"},{"pid":"440ed86b68374bc4f3eafdf9c4ec8ac93dcae099","tid":1977750,"uid":867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:53:19.000Z","msg":"所有電子儀器都唔得"},{"pid":"e5b915798d8fc0747ca7cfb78683ed699ae18cf6","tid":1977750,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:53:46.000Z","msg":"識買一定買有計時錶圈嘅analog watch"},{"pid":"914c76d637e042fee85081cfdf5e82a545b2cc6c","tid":1977750,"uid":226939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:54:00.000Z","msg":"唔比 電子錶響都有機會要寫report 帶翻普通錶啦"},{"pid":"fbc9bae9596d5eb7d3fbf39190e6d3aa8f3fbaeb","tid":1977750,"uid":121199,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:54:11.000Z","msg":"考生手冊寫明唔比，你讀咁多年書最重要既一場試，冇理由搏呢d野<br />\n<br />\n利申：監考員"},{"pid":"7ef458429e8d721d651107ea0f792e534c10bc44","tid":1977750,"uid":230298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:56:19.000Z","msg":"智能手錶一定唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n監考員有責任check的，你俾人發現左扣分、降一個grade就好唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b91b3dc5e253ce485dd6cc95801b55aa01ad84","tid":1977750,"uid":139609,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:56:20.000Z","msg":"唔肯定就唔好戴，去12蚊店買隻頹廢錶戴住先。<br />\n無謂因為咁而比人處分，到時搞完一大輪仲要影響埋心情，影響埋之後嗰幾場考試。<br />\n<br />\n記住聽足考官指示，唔好未收到指示就痴label果啲<br />\n<br />\n考listening要帶兩部收音機"},{"pid":"814fa8d14af360fa5d61c6879be2ec9e05e0feae","tid":1977750,"uid":257285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:56:36.000Z","msg":"明白哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁我都係買隻普通錶就最穩陣"},{"pid":"7ab8684c1e2804ca45eccaa875f5a4c14b53eec5","tid":1977750,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:56:58.000Z","msg":"睇出面個鐘好過啦<br />\n自己戴住仲成日望時間<br />\n壓力仲大"},{"pid":"9a9896f4e0d01d7a080d1ef6a5353ac46b8bd386","tid":1977750,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:57:44.000Z","msg":"幾年前我做過監考就最鍾意捉Smart Watch"},{"pid":"74639842e06566497338181e86826592e5fc986c","tid":1977750,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ab8684c1e2804ca45eccaa875f5a4c14b53eec5","tid":1977750,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:56:58.000Z","msg":"睇出面個鐘好過啦<br />\n自己戴住仲成日望時間<br />\n壓力仲大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"